translationFileNamePattern.description:
Defines how the extension to get the corresponding translation file name. The default value is '${name}(${lang}-${region})', which:
* `${name}`: stands for the source xliff file name;
* `${lang}`: stands for the language;
* `${region}`ï¼š stands for the region where the language in use.
You can define your own pattern by using the above placeholder tags.
